Class ConditionalExpression<O>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.co.strangeskies.mathematics.expression.MutableExpressionImpl<T>

    O - The type of the expression.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Expression<O>, MutableExpression<O>, Observable<Expression<O>>

    public class ConditionalExpression<O>
extends DependentExpression<O>
    An Expression whose primary dependency is conditional on a Boolean Expression dependency. The primary dependency, in this instance, provides the value of this Expression directly.
